<function>

access:   public

name: add

param: string, $key

param: mixed, $val

return: void

</function>

Appends a "read-once" session value to a class and key.

* Parameters:

 * string //$key//: The specific type of information for the class.

 * mixed //$val//: The flash value to add to the key; this will result in the flash becoming an array.

* Returns void